<h2 id="title-jaxsgmcmodular-sgmcmc-in-jax--笔记">title: JaxSGMC：Modular SGMCMC in JAX--笔记</h2>
<h3 id="0摘要">0.摘要</h3>
<p> 我们介绍了 JaxSGMC，这是一个与应用无关的 JAX 随机梯度马尔可夫链蒙特卡罗（SG-MCMC）库。SG-MCMC 方案是一种不确定性量化（UQ）方法，可扩展到大型数据集和高维模型，通过贝叶斯深度学习实现值得信赖的神经网络预测。JaxSGMC 实现了几种最先进的 SG-MCMC 采样器，通过降低从随机优化转换到 SG-MCMC 采样的门槛，促进深度学习中的不确定性量化。此外，JaxSGMC 还允许用户从标准 SG-MCMC 构建模块中构建自定义采样器。由于这种模块化结构，我们预计 JaxSGMC 将加速新型 SG-MCMC 方案的研究，并促进其在广泛领域的应用。</p>
<h3 id="1动机和意义">1.动机和意义</h3>
<p> 过去十年，深度学习模型在多个科学领域取得了显著成功。然而，神经网络（NN）作为数据驱动的黑盒模型，其在训练数据之外的预测可能不准确。为评估预测可信度，不确定性量化（UQ）至关重要，特别是在安全关键型应用中。</p>
<p> 用于神经网络的 UQ 方法包括 Bootstrapping、conformal inference、Deep Ensembles 和 Bayesian 方法。尽管贝叶斯统计为贝叶斯 UQ 提供了理论基础，但经典的基于马尔可夫链蒙特卡罗（MCMC）的方法在计算上成本高昂。随机梯度（SG）MCMC 方案通过对小批量数据的似然梯度进行随机估计，避免了经典 MCMC 中对全数据似然的全面评估，从而显著加快了计算速度，推动了贝叶斯深度学习的发展。</p>
<h3 id="2软件描述">2.软件描述</h3>
<p> 不确定性量化（UQ）库的现状较为分散：</p>
<ul>
<li>一方面是特定领域的库，如 NeuralUQ</li>
<li>另一方面是领域无关的库，如 TensorFlow Probability 和 Pyro。这两个库分别用于 TensorFlow 和 PyTorch，侧重于经典的 HMC 方法和随机变分推断（SVI），其中只实现的随机梯度马尔可夫链蒙特卡罗（SG-MCMC）采样器是 Stochastic Gradient Langevin Dynamics（SGLD）。</li>
</ul>
<p> 然而，这些库的结构目前不支持使用最近提出的 SG-MCMC 算法构建模块，因此，许多新开发的 SG-MCMC 采样器都是作为独立代码发布，并没有利用这些现有库的优势，这就减缓了新型 SG-MCMC 采样器在实践中的应用。</p>
<p> 这项工作引入了与领域无关的 JaxSGMC 库。JaxSGMC 实现了几种最先进的 SG-MCMC 采样器，如 Replica Exchange SG-MCMC 和 AMAGOLD 。</p>
<h4 id="21-贝叶斯建模">2.1 贝叶斯建模</h4>
<p> 一个模型由架构 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\cal {M}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal">M</span></span></span></span></span></span> 和参数 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mtext>𝜽</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">𝜽</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;"></span><span class="mord">𝜽</span></span></span></span> 组成。在深度学习中，这些模型是具有数百万个参数的 NN，如 ResNet 。频率学派机器学习（ML）方法通过损失函数的随机优化来选择好的模型，以获得数据集（如 CIFAR-10）的最优参数集 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover accent="true"><mi>θ</mi><mo>ˉ</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\bar{\theta}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8312em;"></span><span class="mord accent"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8312em;"><span style="top:-3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span></span><span style="top:-3.2634em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="accent-body" style="left:-0.1667em;"><span class="mord">ˉ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>，所选的参数 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover accent="true"><mi>θ</mi><mo>ˉ</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\bar{\theta}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8312em;"></span><span class="mord accent"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8312em;"><span style="top:-3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span></span><span style="top:-3.2634em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="accent-body" style="left:-0.1667em;"><span class="mord">ˉ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 决定了模型的性能和可靠性。</p>
<p> 贝叶斯方法研究后验分布：</p>
<p class="katex-block"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mtable width="100%"><mtr><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="script">D</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mo>∫</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mtext> </mtext><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>θ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="script">D</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mtext> </mtext><mi>d</mi><mi>θ</mi></mrow></mtd><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(1)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">p(y|\mathbf{x}, \mathcal{D}, M) = \int p(y|\mathbf{x}, \theta, M) \, p(\theta|\mathcal{D}, M) \, d\theta \tag{1}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.2222em;vertical-align:-0.8622em;"></span><span class="mop op-symbol large-op" style="margin-right:0.44445em;position:relative;top:-0.0011em;">∫</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">d</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span></span><span class="tag"><span class="strut" style="height:2.2222em;vertical-align:-0.8622em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">1</span></span><span class="mord">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>表示给定输入 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>𝐱</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">𝐱</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4444em;"></span><span class="mord mathbf">x</span></span></span></span> 时模型预测 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>𝑦</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">𝑦</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span></span></span></span> 的不确定性。式（1）并不是单一参数集 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mover accent="true"><mi>θ</mi><mo>ˉ</mo></mover></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\bar{\theta}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8312em;"></span><span class="mord accent"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8312em;"><span style="top:-3em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span></span><span style="top:-3.2634em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="accent-body" style="left:-0.1667em;"><span class="mord">ˉ</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 上，而是考虑了无限多个模型，根据它们与后验分布 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>𝑝</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mtext>𝜽</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">D</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">𝑝(𝜽|\cal D,\cal M)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">𝜽∣</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></span>给出的数据集的一致性进行加权。这个积分在分析上是难以处理的，但可以通过蒙特卡罗积分法，采用有限数量的模型进行估计</p>
<p class="katex-block"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mtable width="100%"><mtr><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="script">D</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>≈</mo><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><msub><mi>N</mi><mtext>models</mtext></msub></munderover><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>y</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo separator="true">;</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>∼</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>θ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="script">D</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mtd><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(2)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">p(y|\mathbf{x}, \mathcal{D}, \mathcal{M}) \approx \sum_{i=1}^{N_{\text{models}}} p(y|\mathbf{x}, \theta_i, \mathcal{M});  \theta_i \sim p(\theta|\mathcal{D}, \mathcal{M})\tag{2}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:3.1229em;vertical-align:-1.2777em;"></span><span class="mop op-limits"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.8452em;"><span style="top:-1.8723em;margin-left:0em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span><span class="mrel mtight">=</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span><span class="mop op-symbol large-op">∑</span></span></span><span style="top:-4.3169em;margin-left:0em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3448em;"><span style="top:-2.3488em;margin-left:-0.109em;margin-right:0.0714em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.5em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size3 size1 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord text mtight"><span class="mord mtight">models</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.1512em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.2777em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mpunct">;</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∼</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span><span class="tag"><span class="strut" style="height:3.1229em;vertical-align:-1.2777em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">2</span></span><span class="mord">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>从后验分布中提取。贝叶斯公式将后验分布</p>
<p class="katex-block"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mtable width="100%"><mtr><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>θ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">D</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">D</mi><mi mathvariant="script">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="script">θ</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mi mathvariant="script">p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="script">θ</mi><mi mathvariant="script">∣</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">D</mi><mi mathvariant="script">∣</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></mfrac><mo>∝</mo><mi>exp</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mo>−</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">U</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="script">θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></mrow></mtd><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(3)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">p(\theta|\cal D, \cal M)=\frac{p(\cal D|\theta, \cal M)p(\theta|\cal M)}{p(\cal D|\cal M)} \propto \exp(-\cal{U}(\theta))\tag{3}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.363em;vertical-align:-0.936em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.427em;"><span style="top:-2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.936em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">∝</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mop">exp</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.09931em;">U</span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mclose">))</span></span></span></span></span><span class="tag"><span class="strut" style="height:2.363em;vertical-align:-0.936em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">3</span></span><span class="mord">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>与似然函数, 先验分布和模型证据联系起来，使分布归一化。</p>
<ul>
<li>似然函数 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">D</mi><mi mathvariant="script">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="script">θ</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">p(\cal D|\theta,M)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span>：模型可能生成数据的概率。</li>
<li>先验分布 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>θ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">p(\theta|\cal M)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span>：编码了模型的先验信息，与数据无关。</li>
<li>模型证据 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">D</mi><mi mathvariant="script">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">p(\cal D|M)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">D</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p> 现代 MCMC 算法通过模拟物理过程（例如，哈密顿或朗之万动力学）来生成样本序列，这些物理过程由势能 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo>−</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">U</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="script">θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">-\cal{U}(\theta)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.09931em;">U</span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span> 的梯度驱动。附加的 MH 步骤接受或拒绝每个提议（proposal），从而使马尔可夫链的平稳分布与后验分布一致。由于梯度 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">∇</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">U</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi mathvariant="script">θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\nabla\cal{U}(\theta)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">∇</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.09931em;">U</span></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span></span> 依赖于所有数据点，需要在模拟的每个时间步进行计算，因此将基于梯度的 MCMC 方法扩展到大数据应用在计算上是不可行的。</p>
<p>与随机梯度下降（SGD）格式类似，SG-MCMC方法采用带噪声的势估计</p>
<p class="katex-block"><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mtable width="100%"><mtr><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">U</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>≈</mo><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mi>N</mi><mi>n</mi></mfrac><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mi>n</mi></munderover><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>−</mo><mi>log</mi><mo>⁡</mo><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>θ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow></mtd><mtd width="50%"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(4)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathcal{U}(\theta) \approx -\frac{N}{n} \sum_{i=1}^{n} \log p(y_i|\mathbf{x}_i, \theta, \mathcal{M}) - \log p(\theta|\mathcal{M})\tag{4}
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.09931em;">U</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≈</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:2.9291em;vertical-align:-1.2777em;"></span><span class="mord">−</span><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.3603em;"><span style="top:-2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">n</span></span></span><span style="top:-3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width:0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top:-3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.10903em;">N</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.686em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mop op-limits"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.6514em;"><span style="top:-1.8723em;margin-left:0em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span><span class="mrel mtight">=</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span style="top:-3.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span><span class="mop op-symbol large-op">∑</span></span></span><span style="top:-4.3em;margin-left:0em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:3.05em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">n</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:1.2777em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mop">lo<span style="margin-right:0.01389em;">g</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mop">lo<span style="margin-right:0.01389em;">g</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span><span class="tag"><span class="strut" style="height:2.9291em;vertical-align:-1.2777em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">4</span></span><span class="mord">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p> 基于随机的 mini-batch 取 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.4306em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">n</span></span></span></span> 个数据点。这些近似会使平稳分布产生偏差，从而使传统的 Metropolis-Hastings (MH) 校正不再适用。尽管如此，经典的随机梯度马尔可夫链蒙特卡罗 (SG-MCMC) 方法通过适当退火模拟时间步长 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>t</mi><mo>→</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Delta t \to 0</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">Δ</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">→</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6444em;"></span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span> 并向随机梯度中添加适量噪声，能够实现渐近正确的平稳分布。</p>
<h4 id="22-软件结构">2.2 软件结构</h4>
<p> 这张图展示了 JaxSGMC 中软件模块之间的关系。每个模块包含构建 SG-MCMC 采样器的算法构建块。简而言之，一个 SGMCMC 采样器重复以下步骤：</p>
<ul>
<li>（a） 检索当前过程参数（<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>t</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\Delta t</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord">Δ</span><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span></span></span></span>、温度等）</li>
<li>（b） 通过势函数 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">U</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathcal{U}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.6833em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.09931em;">U</span></span></span></span> 从当前样本 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\theta_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 开始模拟过程</li>
<li>（c） 处理获得的提议</li>
<li>（d） 保存新的样本 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>θ</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\theta_{i+1}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.9028em;vertical-align:-0.2083em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span><span class="mbin mtight">+</span><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2083em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
</ul>
<p><img src="file:///g:\MyBlog\blog\source\_posts\G:%5CMyBlog%5Cblog%5Csource%5Cpic%5CjaxSGMC%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84.png" alt="jaxSGMC软件架构">
以下是 JaxSGMC 的主要组件和工作流程：</p>
<ol>
<li><code>potential.py</code> 模块与对数似然计算</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>用户提供的模型（如神经网络）可在 JAX 中转换。</li>
<li>对于模型参数 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\theta_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 和观测 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">(\mathbf{x}_k, y_k)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>，对数似然函数计算对数概率 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi>p</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>y</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">∣</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="bold">x</mi><mi>k</mi></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo separator="true">,</mo><mi mathvariant="script">M</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">p(y_k|\mathbf{x}_k, \theta_i, \mathcal{M})</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathnormal">p</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">y</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord">∣</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathbf">x</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3361em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.03148em;">k</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mpunct">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal">M</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>。</li>
<li><code>potential.py</code> 模块计算势函数 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="script">U</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\mathcal{U}(\theta_i)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.09931em;">U</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 或其随机估计。</li>
</ul>
<ol start="2">
<li>函数式编程与 JAX 集成</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>采用函数式编程风格，利用 JAX 的函数变换和自动微分功能。</li>
<li>执行对数似然的批量评估，计算随机梯度 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">∇</mi><mi mathvariant="script">U</mi><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\nabla \mathcal{U}(\theta)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord">∇</span><span class="mord mathcal" style="margin-right:0.09931em;">U</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span>，运行多个马尔可夫链。</li>
</ul>
<ol start="3">
<li><code>data.py</code> 模块与大数据处理</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>通过 JAX 的主机回调模块，高效处理来自数据加载器（DataLoaders）的数据。</li>
<li>支持多种小批量组装方法和数据源集成。</li>
</ul>
<ol start="4">
<li><code>io.py</code> 模块与样本存储</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>高效存储深度神经网络的参数样本 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>θ</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\theta_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8444em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.02778em;">θ</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0278em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>。</li>
<li>支持在 JIT 编译的 SG-MCMC 算法中收集和保存大量样本。</li>
</ul>
<ol start="5">
<li>核心组件与模块化设计</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li><code>data.py</code> 、<code>adaption.py</code>和 <code>potential.py</code> 模块提供 SG-MCMC 算法的核心组件。</li>
<li>采样部分分为  <code>solver.py</code>（处理提议）和<code>integrator.py</code>（模拟物理过程）。</li>
</ul>
<ol start="6">
<li>调度部分与算法运行</li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>调度部分提供运行构建算法的一般入口点。</li>
<li><code>scheduler.py</code> 连接过程参数的调度与马尔可夫链接口，并保存状态或样本。</li>
<li>支持反馈循环以实现自适应步长方案。</li>
</ul>
<h4 id="22-软件功能">2.2 软件功能</h4>
<p>该包实现了两个 API 层级：</p>
<ul>
<li>首先，在 <code>alias.py</code> 中构建了一个高级接口，这个接口旨在让用户可以轻松地从随机优化器切换到 SG-MCMC 采样器，支持多种流行的 SG-MCMC 采样器。包括：
<ul>
<li>pSGLD</li>
<li>随机梯度哈密顿蒙特卡洛 (SGHMC)</li>
<li>复制交换 SG-MCMC (reSGLD)</li>
<li>随机梯度引导蒙特卡洛 (SGGMC)</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>第二个 API 层的设计灵感来自于随机优化库 Optax 。该层允许更高级的用户将SG-MCMC 构建块组合起来，以创建针对特定问题量身定制的自定义采样器。</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="3-实际例子">3 实际例子</h3>
